                        <a class="nav-link px-0 py-1" href="#liability">7. Liability</a>
                        <a class="nav-link px-0 py-1" href="#ip">8. Intellectual Property</a>
                        <a class="nav-link px-0 py-1" href="#changes">9. Changes</a>
                        <a class="nav-link px-0 py-1" href="#law">10. Governing Law</a>
                        <a class="nav-link px-0 py-1" href="#contact">11. Contact</a>
                    </nav>
                </div>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-xl-9">
            <div id="acceptance" class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">1) Acceptance</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        By accessing or using our ticket booking platform (“Service”), you agree to these Terms & Conditions.
                        If you do not agree, please do not use the Service.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="accounts" class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">2) Accounts & Security</h3>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and password.</li>
                        <li>You must provide accurate and up-to-date information.</li>
                        <li>Notify us immediately of any unauthorized use or security breach.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="booking" class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">3) Booking & Payment</h3>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>All bookings are subject to availability and partner/operator confirmation.</li>
                        <li>Prices may include taxes/fees; any additional charges will be shown before payment.</li>
                        <li>Payments are processed via secure payment gateways; we don’t store full card details.</li>
                        <li>Once a booking is confirmed, your e-ticket or confirmation will be available by email and/or profile.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="cancellation" class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">4) Cancellation & Refunds</h3>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Cancellation windows and fees depend on the operator/event policy.</li>
                        <li>No-show may result in forfeiture of the fare.</li>
                        <li>Refunds (if eligible) are processed to the original payment method within a reasonable timeframe.</li>
                        <li>For rescheduling, operator rules and fare differences may apply.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="eventtravel" class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">5) Event & Travel Rules</h3>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Carry valid ID and the ticket/PNR as required by the venue or carrier.</li>
                        <li>Arrive before the reporting time; late arrival may void boarding/entry.</li>
                        <li>Follow baggage, conduct, and safety guidelines of the operator/venue.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="prohibited" class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">6) Prohibited Uses</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        You agree not to misuse the Service, including but not limited to fraud, scraping, interfering with
                        security, reverse engineering, or violating applicable laws and policies.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="liability" class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">7) Liability</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        To the fullest extent permitted by law, we are not liable for indirect or consequential damages,
                        operator actions, schedule changes, cancellations due to force majeure, or issues outside our control.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="ip" class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">8) Intellectual Property</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        Content on the Service (logos, graphics, text) is protected by intellectual property laws. You may
                        not copy, modify, or distribute without permission.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="changes" class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">9) Changes to These Terms</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        We may update these Terms to reflect changes in our Service or legal requirements. We’ll post the
                        latest version here with the updated date above.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="law" class="card border-0 shadow-sm mb-3">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">10) Governing Law</h3>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        These Terms are governed by the laws of your local jurisdiction unless otherwise required by law.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div id="contact" class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                <div class="card-body p-4">
                    <h3 class="fw-bold">11) Contact</h3>
                    <ul class="mb-0">
                        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a></li>
                        <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+8801XXXXXXXXX">+880 1782025121</a></li>
                        <li>Address: Sector 10, Uttara, Dhaka</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
